These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, horror, epic, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, country, folk, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, indian, malaysian, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship, motorbike, airplane
1. the indian is the fan of disco##1
2. the malaysian is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
3. the indian is the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the russian##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching epic movies##1
7. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
8. the russian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | disaster   | time-travel  | epic  |
| Music-Genre   | country    | disco    | electronic      | folk    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | indian | malaysian | russian |
| Transport     | airplane  | snowmobile       | ship    | motorbike     |

