.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, reading, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, spy, time-travel, crime
4 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, guinea-pig, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, biathlon, climbing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's sport is handball##2
6. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching crime movies and the owner of the rabbit##2
7. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
8. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking | hiking    | reading  | rock-climbing    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | spy  | crime  | time-travel |
| Pet           | rabbit      | guinea-pig       | hamster      | fish       |
| Sport         | biathlon    | rowing | climbing | handball |

