.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cranberry, pineapple, broccoli
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku, dancing, collecting
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, scientist, photographer, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, skateboard, bike, bus
1. the photographer is the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the security-guard##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the scientist is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
7. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person eating spinach is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person eating pineapple and the scientist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | cranberry | pineapple     | spinach   | broccoli     |
| Hobby       | sudoku   | card-games   | dancing | collecting |
| Job         | fisherman   | photographer | security-guard       | scientist    |
| Transport   | bike    | skateboard | boat  | bus    |

