 3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is the lawyer##1
 8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 9. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the journalist is between the owner of the fish and the firefighter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | freelancer  | firefighter | journalist     | lawyer |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | western  | comedy | animation       |
| Pet           | turtle       | horse    | rabbit      | fish           |
| Sport         | snowboarding | handball   | baseball   | lacrosse         |

