 7. the coach is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the photographer is the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person eating pepper is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
10. the person watching satire movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1

