2. the bartender is between the fan of hip-hop and the french##2
3. the american is between the person who's sport is swimming and the spanish##2
4. the electrician is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the american is the american##1
6. the spanish is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the spanish is on the left of the mechanic##1
8. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
9. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
