 4. the fan of indie is the person driving the car##1
 5. the polish is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 7. the colombian is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
10. the french is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | scientific | musical  | mystery  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | indie   | ambient | d&b    |
