The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, mystery, horror
4 different pets are kept: pony, rat, turtle, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, bus, motorbike
1. the person watching adventure movies is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the bus and the person watching action movies##2
6. the person drinking 7up is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | 7up  | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk    | fanta  |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | adventure   | action | mystery |
| Pet           | pony       | turtle   | rat        | mouse  |
| Transport     | bus | tram | snowmobile         | motorbike |

