 4. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 5. the fan of classical is the person eating potato##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the left of the paramedic##1
 8. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
 9. the manager is between the security-guard and the person who's sport is basketball##2
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
