 4. the person eating cranberry is the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the owner of the cat is between the person eating cranberry and the person eating raspberry##2
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person eating cranberry and the person eating raspberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea    | juice    | cola      | milk |
| Food       | cranberry        | zucchini       | raspberry       | papaya     |
| Hobby      | dancing | camping | card-games | singing        |
