 3. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the lizard##2
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating tomato##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the scooter##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | cabbage  | tomato | radish     | watermelon     |
